2. ✅ Check units — is the table in thousands? millions? Convert if needed
3. ✅ Check the row label — "Total capital" ≠ "Capital account"
4. ✅ Check the date — calendar year → June bulletin of NEXT year; fiscal year → December bulletin
5. ✅ If the answer seems too simple or too round, double-check the source data

